Lesiones con perturbaci\'f3n s\'edquica (art.335).
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s23 \f3\lang1034\cgrid \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Hurto calificado (art.350).
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s23 \f3\lang1034\cgrid \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}}\pard \s23\qj\li567\ri-700\widctlpar\tx360\tx567{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls5\pnrnot0\pnf3\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'b7}}\ls5\adjustright {\i\fs24\ul\lang1034 
